    "The returning signal is sensed by the photodetector.",
    "The signal is filtered by fast electronics and the difference between transmitted and received signal is estimated.",
    "The exact range is calculated based on this difference by the sensor model.",
    "Signal processing is used to compensate for differences in variations of the transmitted and reflected signals because of surface materials.",
    "The outputs of LiDAR are 3D point clouds corresponding to scanned environments, and intensities corresponding to the reflected laser energies [56]."
